{"tid":2273102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李寧旗下私募基金    斥 10 億收購 Clarks 多數股權","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T15:19:49.000Z","uid":263197,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"00520cc945844c141d8b65e7a444389e562e28b2","tid":2273102,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"節錄：<br />\n大陸體育品牌「奧運冠軍及李寧公司」的創辦人李寧，其擔任主席的私募基金萊恩資本（LionRock Capital）昨晚宣布，收購英國知名百年鞋履品牌 Clarks 的多數股權，而 Clarks 家族將保留少數股權。根據《金融時報》引述 Clarks 家族成員表示，交易作價涉約 1 億英鎊，即約 10.09 億港元，但沒有透露交易後家族仍持有多少股份權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%A7%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E7%A7%81%E5%8B%9F%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E6%96%A5-10-%E5%84%84%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC-clarks-%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AF%25A7%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%258B%259F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E6%2596%25A5-10-%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC-clarks-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8hfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=01a2c501\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AF%25A7%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%258B%259F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E6%2596%25A5-10-%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC-clarks-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A&h=fe4be5bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%A7%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E7%A7%81%E5%8B%9F%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E6%96%A5-10-%E5%84%84%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC-clarks-%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A</a>"},{"pid":"bc8dec8e04cc795599a48200e49df28334f795b2","tid":2273102,"uid":151057,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:23:18.00